    "summary": "The user, acting as a debate coach, explicitly asks the assistant to \"steelman\" one specific side of an immigration debate (pro-enforcement). The assistant complies by providing strong, unhedged arguments for increased border security, economic protectionism, and the moral necessity of enforcement, without providing any counter-perspectives or acknowledging the complexity of the issue.",
